PrecisDesignation of the Minister of COMMUNICATIONS as the "appropriate Minister" with respect to the OFFICE OF THE CO-ORDINATOR, STATUS OF WOMEN who shall co-ordinate policy with respect to the status of women and administer related programs, and to that end, be the Minister responsible for the Advisory Council on the Status of Women.

precis:
Designation of the Minister of COMMUNICATIONS as the "appropriate Minister"
with respect to the OFFICE OF THE CO-ORDINATOR, STATUS OF WOMEN who shall
co-ordinate policy with respect to the status of women and administer
related programs, and to that end, be the Minister responsible for the
Advisory Council on the Status of Women.
